text: Nicky Jam : El Ganador, the music bio series that tells the life story of popular award - winning reggaeton singer songwriter Nicky Jam, makes its debut on Netflix, but not on Telemundo. The network previously announced it would air the series first during the summer, with Netflix following suit. But now, it's the streaming service that gets the first shot at sharing the story of the rise, fall and rebirth of the hit - making reggaeton singer. Nicky Jam : El Ganador, will be available on the streamer starting Friday, November 30 in Latin America and Spain. Telemundo has not set a date yet for its release in the United States and Puerto Rico, where it holds the rights to the series.
